title: Haggard Wulf - Devil Johnston EP (2011) [320 Kbps]
description:
Haggard Wulf are a 2-piece band from Morgantown, WV, who bring together
a mixture of blues, rockabilly and punk rock. Their sound and style is
diverse, bringing a very full sound to the table. They have a very strong DIY
ethic, much like the punk bands of the late 70s and early 80s.

This 3 song EP is comprised of Daniel Johnston covers that were recorded for a
compilation in conjunction with the Daniel Johnston art exhibit at Blast Gallery in Teaneck, NJ. Released on November 11, 2011 by 'Nuff Said Records.

Tracklist:

1. Devil Town (1:27)
2. Wicked World (2:47)
3. Don't Play Cards With Satan (3:43)
